    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation at a lower price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some minor paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all electronics and the air conditioning still function properly. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need routine maintenance like new tires and a brake service in the near future.",
      "price": 19500.0,
